  (text "SENSING: 2x 1m0 2512 in parallel = 0.5m shunt (sourcing-friendly; cal absorbs\nthe split). INA240A3 x100 -> 0.05V/A, 1.5V @ 30A (A4 would exceed the DAC's\n2.5V ceiling - docs/08 s.4). V divider /12 (110K/10K). Droop: 267K + TMUX1101\ninto the V_MEAS node, ~20mV/A; fw applies x0.9668 to V_ref in droop modes."
    (at 219.71 172.72 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)))
    (uuid fffb9e77-7e36-409b-b77d-3cb1fe3859bb)
  )

